# Key-Based Path Recording System

## Goal
Replace action-type recording with keypress recording for precise path replay.

## Current vs New Approach

| Item | Current | New |
|------|---------|-----|
| Format | `[x, y, action]` | `[x, y, timestamp, keys[]]` |
| Recording | Detect action from keys | Record raw keys |
| Execution | Decide keys from action | Replay recorded keys |

---

## Proposed Changes

### [MODIFY] [RouteRecorderService.cs](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Services/RouteRecorderService.cs)

**RoutePoint class changes:**
```csharp
public class RoutePoint
{
    public SdPointF Position { get; set; }
    public float Timestamp { get; set; }        // Relative time (seconds)
    public List<string> Keys { get; set; }      // ["left", "up", "space"]
    public ActionType Action => DeriveAction(); // Derived from Keys
}
```

**Recording changes:**
- Track currently pressed keys via `GetAsyncKeyState`
- Record point when keys change OR position changes significantly
- Store relative timestamp from recording start

---

### [NEW] [PathExecutor.cs](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Services/PathExecutor.cs)

New service for path playback:
- Tracks currently held keys
- Syncs keys to match target point's keys
- Advances to next point when position reached

---

### [MODIFY] [MapData.cs](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Models/Map/MapData.cs)

Add new path format that includes timestamps and keys.

---

### [MODIFY] [MainForm.cs](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/UI/MainForm.cs)

Integrate PathExecutor for path playback mode.

---

